sequenceDiagram
  participant Cron
  participant Worker
  participant DB
  participant LLM
  participant Email
  participant Push
  participant User

  Cron->>Worker: generate due briefings
  Worker->>DB: load users due for delivery
  Worker->>DB: load raw items for inactive window
  Worker->>Worker: cluster and rank
  Worker->>LLM: summarize selected clusters
  LLM-->>Worker: validated JSON candidates
  Worker->>DB: save briefing and items
  Worker->>Email: send email briefing
  Email-->>User: morning briefing email
  alt push enabled
    Worker->>Push: send briefing ready notification
    Push-->>User: web push notification
  end
  Worker->>DB: save delivery logs
